@node GEMST "Gemstone Mine"

@{b}Gemstone Mine@{ub}

Rarity  = WL(U)
Type    = Land
Artist  = Brom

Text(WL): When Gemstone Mine comes into play, put three mining counters
          on it.
          <T>, Remove a mining counter from Gemstone Mine: Add one mana
          of any color to your mana pool. If there are no mining counters
          on Gemstone Mine, bury it.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_G.guide/GEMST}

@endnode
@node LOTUS "Lotus Vale"

@{b}Lotus Vale@{ub}

Rarity  = WL(R)
Type    = Land
Artist  = John Avon

Text(WL): When Lotus Vale comes into play, sacrifice two untapped lands
          or bury Lotus Vale.
          <T>: Add three mana of any one color to your mana pool.

Flavor Text: @{i}At what price beauty?@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_L.guide/LOTVA}

@endnode
@node SCORC "Scorched Ruins"

@{b}Scorched Ruins@{ub}

Rarity  = WL(R)
Type    = Land
Artist  = John Avon

Text(WL): When Scorched Ruins comes into play, sacrifice two untapped
          lands or bury Scorched Ruins.
          <T>: Add four colorless mana to your mana pool.

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node WINDI "Winding Canyons"

@{b}Winding Canyons@{ub}

Rarity  = WL(R)
Type    = Land
Artist  = John Avon

Text(WL): <T>: Add one colorless mana to your mana pool.
          <2T>: Until end of turn, you may play creature
          cards whenever you could play instants.

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

